data.description: Bring your Backup Offers for this 1538 square feet, this residence features 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, with a split bedroom floorpan and oversized 3 car garage, providing ample space for comfortable living. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas.The heart of this home is the well-appointed kitchen, showcasing granite counters, and glass backsplash, perfect for culinary enthusiasts. Step outside to a covered patio, ideal for al fresco dining or simply enjoying the desert breeze. The property is not just a home; it's a lifestyle. Soak in the Arizona sunshine and reduce your carbon footprint with solar panels and capabilities to charge your electric car. Embrace community living with easy access to the nearby Community Park, a hub for recreation and social activities. Additionally, benefit from being part of the renowned Amphi School District, ensuring quality education for your family.  Don't miss the opportunity to call this Oro Valley gem your home.
